it would cause trying to get the higher AC stuff like fierce heraldic (rallos zek) doh...<br>
<br>
Can anyone suggest a BP with similar stats I may use? (probably for around 30-40k.. I think Cobalt is out of the question) Or is my only option to to hit the planes?<br>
<br>
