 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=129424">Khanate</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=531451">Warhead</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xiththewizard>Xith the Wizard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/27/03 7:09:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4923.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ogre Agnostic problems..</span><hr size=1> Um ... being agnostic isnt a problem.<br>
<br>
Why not look into some of the non diety cultural<br>
<br>
Or MQ Champs or Myrm.<br>
<br>
At 45, your not even of a level to use most high end stuff yet.<br>
<br>
At 45, your EXPing in DL/KC I assume, er, dont really need a high AC for those spots.<br>
<br>
Why is cobalt out ??<br>
<br>
Did you make an ogre just cause someone said they make the best warriors ??<br>
<br>
Cultural BP kinda sucks next to the rest of the peices.  yes cobalt is still a better BP.<br>
<br>
Shissar BP is by far better than most warriors will see till the 50s.  <br>
<br>
Dont assume your gonna get the best gear before your ready for it, most of the high end tanks that post here have been playing the class for years, and it takes years to get the kind of kit they have.<br>
<br>
Level, gear comes in time.<br>
<br>
At 45 you shouldnt be concerning yourself with getting better gear, you should focus on leveling, if you hit the 60s and are still wearing Shiss BP, then ask again.<br>
<br>
I wore Barbed ringmail till i was 56, no reason your shissar BP wont hold you till at least then.<br>
<br>
oh, and post a magelo before you ask about equiptment questions.  Or youll get basically the same kind of post i just gave.  Sarcastic ones telling you stuff you really dont wanna hear.<br>
<br>
Theres nothing wrong with being agnostic.  Just means you cant wear Fierce Heraldic (OH GOD NO), which means you just have to find another option which really aint that hard to do.<br>
<br>
I know many warriors than break 8khp with no cultural at all.<br>
<br>
Cultural is a crutch, dont make your toon around armor, but make your armor selections around your toon.<br>
<br>
Coming here with questions like this force me to ask ... twink right ... thought so. <br>
<br>
you cant hit the planes till 46 .... and yes ... PoG armor is the way to go for you once you reach that point, PoG or Thurg (champs).  If i were you, id focus on that, PoG or Quest stuff.  and forget about FH stuff, its nice, but theres better out there. <p>Master Xith N'Shezbenon<br>
