<br>
There is a magelo link on my post for Warhead which is my warrior ( I shall illuminate it in bright neon lights for next time!).<br>
<br>
Yes he is twinked I am not bothered about saying that, I am sure that a lot of people who will criticise that are probably being hypocritical. My other characters I have played to 50+ were not twinked, I just do not have the time now to dedicate doing another one. Sorry I strayed from the path of untwinkable holiness that you took, forgive me I have sinned <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I am not going to suddenly restart the guy now (as you are probably assuming), I will work to get planar armor like you suggested. <br>
<br>
I made an ogre because of all the barbarian warriors I saw walking about, I could have easily made any other class I just happen to like ogre's simple as that. You know ogre's have advantages and disadvantages like any other class. The agnostic choice probably reflects my own personal beliefs.<br>
<br>
I know I could wear shissar to 56 I am not saying there is anything wrong with that that is great, I just happen to like equipping new gear nothing wrong with that is there?  One person in my guild happens to have more use for the shissar and I offered to give them that when I bought a new BP, so I thought I would buy something higher AC, or shall I buy a barbed ringmail and wear it so people don't point and go &quot;bad twink!&quot;.<br>
<br>
Cobalt isn't out of the question, I just don't think I can afford it i'd love the BP no doubt.<br>
<br>
Thanks for the suggestions man , no need to jump down my throat.<br>
<br>
