<br>
On the subject of twinking myself with the shissar BP btw, my group and I were in the grey and I won the roll on the item from the named Revanant (Szzhznit? I can't spell that) with my 45 WAR (relying on EB being cast for me as I don't have the amulet of the grey wastes yet). <br>
<br>
Before I got it, I was using an acrylia plate which cost me 800pp (good deal), there's no way I would have bought the Shissar BP for 7-8k on Brell for no gain in raw AC over the acrylia.  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=129424">Khanate</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=531451">Warhead</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gartogggamorean@thesteelwarrior>Gartogg Gamorean</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 38<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/27/03 10:44:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4923.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: options</span><hr size=1> Being Agnostic is a huge disadvantage if your not in a high end guild.  Say you pay 30k for thurg MQ, what do you do when you get an upgrade? destroy the thurg and say goodbye to 30k, what does the person with FH do? sell to another person and recoup probably half the purchase price.<br>
  <br>
Anyone who thinks being an agnostic ogre isn't more difficult gear wise than a rallos one is either beyond cultural armor, has never played one or is ignorant, I would have replace almost ever piece of my armor with FH if I were a rallos warrior, instead I have replaced maybe 2 with agnostic usable stuff as it costs generally 5 times as much as equvalent FH.<br>
<br>
To answer your question:<br>
<br>
Heavy Rubicite BP (25k on xegony)<br>
Tae EW Plate BP (smithed and component drop rates have been uped recently not sure on price)<br>
Hurricane Plate BP (tier 2/3 smithed, not sure on price)<br>
Night Terror Plate BP<br>
<br>
None of the above 4 is superiour to FH and all cost more, everyone but the Heavy Rubi costs probably twice as much, but yeah agnostic isn't a disadvantage /boggle.<br>
<br>
